*
*---- act defproc: foo<> -----
* raw ports:  p q r
*
.subckt foo p q r
*.PININFO p:I q:I r:O
*.POWER VDD Vdd
*.POWER GND GND
*.POWER NSUB GND
*.POWER PSUB Vdd
*
* --- node flags ---
*
* r (combinational)
* v (combinational)
*
* --- end node flags ---
*
M0_N r u Vdd Vdd pch W=0.3U L=0.06U
M1_N v u Vdd Vdd pch W=0.3U L=0.06U
M2_N #3 u GND GND nch W=0.15U L=0.06U
M3_N r p #3 GND nch W=0.15U L=0.06U
M4_N v q #3 GND nch W=0.15U L=0.06U
.ends
*---- end of process: foo<> -----
